<msContents>
  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
  <locus from="1r"/>
  <title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam">The Testament of Our Lord</title>
  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ኪዳን፡ ዘእግዚእነ፡ ወመድኃኒነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ። ኮነ፡ እንከ፡ እምድኅረ፡ ተንሥአ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡
  እምነ፡ ምውታን፡ አስተርአየነ፡ ወተዓገሠ፡ እምቶማስ፡ ወማቴዎስ፡ ወዮሐንስ፡ ወተፈዊሰነ፡ ከመ፡ ተንሥአ፡ ሊቅነ፡ ወወደቅነ፡ በገጽነ፡ ወባረክናሁ፡ ዘአድኃነነ፡
በኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ እግዚእነ። አብ፡ ዘቀደሰ፡ ዓለመ፡ ወፍርሃት፡ በሕቁ፡ አኃዘነ፡ ወነበርነ፡ ውዱቃኒነ፡ ውስተ፡ ምድር፡ ከመ፡ እንተ፡ ሰብእ፡ ምጽልዋን።
ወአንቢሮ፡ እዴሁ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ለለ፩እምውስቴትነ፡ አንሥአነ፡ እንዘ፡ ይብል፡ ለምንት፡ ከመዝ፡ ይወድቅ፡ ልብክሙ፡ ወበሕቁ፡ ትትሐወቁ፡
ኢተአምሩኑ፡ ከመ፡ ዘፈነወኒ፡ ይክል፡ መንክራተ፡ ገቢረ፡ ለመድኃኒት፡ ላዕሌሆሙ፡ ለእለ፡ እምልብ፡ የአምኑ፡ ይእዜኒኬ፡ ኢትኩኑ፡ ድንዙዛነ፡ አላ፡ ከመ፡
ውሉደ፡ ብርሃን፡ ሰአልዎ፡ ለአቡየ፡ ዘበሰማያት። መንፈስ፡ አእምሮ፡ ወጽንዕ፡ ወይሁበክሙ፡ ወይጼግወክሙ፡ መንፈሰ፡ ቅዱሰ፡ ከመ፡ ተሀልዉ፡ ምስሌየ፡ እስከ፡ ለዓለም።</incipit>
  <textLang mainLang="gez"/>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
<locus from="1r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter1">Of the Holy Spirit</title>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#1r"/>አውሣዕናሁ፡ ወንቤ፡ ምንትኑ፡ ውእቱ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ወአይ፡ ኃይል፡ ዘትብል፡ ሰአልዎ፡ ለአቡየለ።</incipit>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
<locus from="1r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter2">Of the signs of the end of the world</title>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#1r"/>አውሣእነ፡ ወንቤሎ፡ እግዚእ፡ ይእዜሂ፡ ንፈቱ፡ ንጠይቅ፡ ምግባራተ፡ ትእምርት፡ ዘፍጻሜሁ፡ ለዓለም፡ ከመ፡
ናእምር፡ ወለእመ፡ ሠምረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ድልዋነ፡ ንኩን፡ ንሕነሂ፡ ወእለሂ፡ ይሰምዑነ፡ ያእምሩ።</incipit>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
<locus from="1r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter3">Of the prodigies which shall happen</title>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#1r"/>በእንተ፡ ትእምርት፡ ዘይከውን።</incipit>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4">
<locus from="1v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter4">Of the elect in the last days</title>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#1v"/>በእንተ፡ ኅሩያን፡ እለ፡ ይከውኑ፡ በደኃሪ፡ መዋዕል።</incipit>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5">
<locus from="1v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter5">What shall happen to the countries</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#1v"/>በእንተ፡ ዘይከውን፡ ላዕለ፡ በሓውርት።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6">
<locus from="2r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter6">Of the Antichrist</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#2r"/>በእንተ፡ ትእምርተ፡ ሐሳዌ፡ መሲሕ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7">
<locus from="2r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter7">Discourse of our Lord to his disciples</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#2r"/>በእንተ፡ ዘነገሮሙ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ለሐዋርያት። ነገርኩክሙ፡
ዘንተ፡ ኵሎ፡ ከመ፡ ኀበ፡ ሖርክሙ፡ ወፈተንክሙ፡ መንፈሰ፡ የውሓት፡ ትንግርዎሙ፡ ዘይደሉ፡ ወዘይኄይስ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.8">
<locus from="2r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter8">Reply of our Lord to Mary, Martha and Salome</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#2r"/>በእንተ፡ ዘአውሥኦን፡ እግዚእነ፡ ለማርያ፡ ወለማርታ፡ ወለሰሎሜ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.9">
<locus from="2v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter9">Of what shall be given to the strong</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#2v"/>በእንተ፡ ዘይትወሀብ፡ ለጽኑዓን።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.10">
<locus from="2v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter10">Of the building of a church</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#2v"/>በእንተ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ቀኖና፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ መፍትው፡ ከመዝ፡ ትኩን፡ 1።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.11">
<locus from="3r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter11">Of the ordination of a bishop</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#3r"/>በእንተ፡ ዘይሠየም፡ ጳጳስ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.12">
<locus from="3r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter12">Prayer at the ordination of a bishop</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#3r"/>ጸሎተ፡ ሢመተ፡ ጳጳስ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.13">
<locus from="3v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter13">That the bishop shall be diligent in sacrifice and prayer</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#3v"/>በእንተ፡ ከመ፡ ይኩን፡ እስትርኩበ፡ ጳጳስ፡ ለምሥዋዕ፡ ወለጸሎት።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.14">
<locus from="3v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter14">That he should teach in the church</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#3v"/>በእንተ፡ ዘይሜሠር፡ በቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.15">
<locus from="3r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter15">Of the teaching of the fundamental doctrines of Christianity</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#3r"/>በእንተ፡ ትምህርተ፡ ምቅቃም።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.16">
<locus from="4r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1100Anapho">Order of the Holy Eucharist</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#4r"/>በእንተ፡ ሥርዓተ፡ ቍርባንም።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.17">
<locus from="5r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter17">Prayers of the faithful whilst and after receiving</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#5r"/>ጸሎት፡ ዘይጼልዩ፡ ምእመናን፡ ፩፩ተመጢዎ፡ አኰቴተ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.18">
<locus from="5r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter18">Prayer of the deacon after all the people have received</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#5r"/>ወእምድኅረ፡ ተመጠዉ፡ ኵሉ፡ ሕዝብ፡ ይብል፡ ዲያቆን።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.19">
<locus from="5r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter19">Prayer of the bishop</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#5r"/>ጸሎት፡ እምኅረ፡ ተመጠዉ፡ አኰቴተ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ይበል፡ ከመዝ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.20">
<locus from="5r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter20">Prayer over the oil for anointing the sick</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#5r"/>ጸሎት፡ ዲበ፡ ቅብዕ፡ ለድውያን።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.21">
<locus from="5r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter21">Of the praises of the congregation</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#5r"/>በእንተ፡ ስብሐተ፡ ማኅበር።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.22">
<locus from="6r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2444Temher">Order of the Holy Eucharist</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#6r"/>በእንተ፡ ትምህርተ፡ ኅቡኣት፡ ቅድመ፡ ዘትትነገር፡ እምጵርስፎራ፡ ለምእመናን፡ ዘይትነበብ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.23">
<locus from="7r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter23">Ordination of a priest</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#7r"/>በእንተ፡ ሢመተ፡ ቀሲስ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.24">
<locus from="7r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter24">Prayer at the ordination of a priest</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#7r"/>ጸሎተ፡ ሢመተ፡ ቀሲስ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.25">
<locus from="7r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter25">That a priest should devote himself to the altar and prayer</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#7r"/>በእንተ፡ ቀሲስ፡ ዘከመ፡ ያስተሐምም፡ ለምሥዋዕ፡ ጸሎታት።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.26">
<locus from="7r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter26">Of the rule of the priest</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#7r"/>በእንተ፡ ሥርዓተ፡ ቀሲስ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.27">
<locus from="7v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter27">Of those who hear and are diligent</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#7v"/>በእንተ፡ እሉ፡ እለ፡ ይሰምዑ፡ ወያስተሐምሙ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.28">
<locus from="7r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter28">Of those who are saved and of those who perish</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#7v"/>በእንተ፡ እለ፡ ይደኅኑ፡ ወበእንተ፡ እለ፡ ይትኃጐሉ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.29">
<locus from="7v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter29">That the priest should visit the sick</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#7v"/>በእንተ፡ መፍትው፡ ቀሲስ፡ ከመ፡ ያንሶሱ፡ ኀበ፡ ድውያን።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.30">
<locus from="8r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter30">Ordination of a deacon</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#8r"/>በእንተ፡ ሢመተ፡ ዲያቆን።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.31">
<locus from="8r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter31">Of the duties of the deacon</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#4r"/>በእንተ፡ ዲያቆን፡ ይትለአክ፡ ወእንግዳ፡ ይትወከፍ፡ ሥርዓተ፡ ቍርባንም።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.32">
<locus from="8r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter32">Of the number of priests, deacons and sub-deacons in a church</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#4r"/>በእንተ፡ ሥርዓተ፡ ቍርባንም።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.33">
<locus from="8r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter33">Order of the Holy Eucharist</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#8r"/>በእንተ፡ ሚመጠን፡ መፍትው፡ ቀሳውስት፡ ወዲያቆናት፡ ወንፍቀ፡ ዲያቆናት፡ ዘይቀውም፡ ለቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.34">
<locus from="9r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter34">Of the order of service in church</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#9r"/>በእንተ፡ ሥርዓተ፡ ቅኔ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.35">
<locus from="9r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter35">Ordination of a deacon</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#9r"/>በእንተ፡ ሢመተ፡ ዲያቆን።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.36">
<locus from="9r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter36">Of widows attached to the service of the church</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#4r"/>በእንተ፡ መዓስብ፡ ትነብር፡ ለመልእክት፡ ኅሪትም።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.37">
<locus from="9v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter37">Prayer for the widows</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#9v"/>ጸሎት፡ ለመኣስብ፡ እንተ፡ ለመልእክት፡ ተሠይመት።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.38">
<locus from="10r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter38">Prayer of the widows</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#10r"/>ከመዝ፡ ትጸሊ፡ መዓስብ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.39">
<locus from="10r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter39">Ordination of the sub-deacon</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#10r"/>በእንተ፡ ንፍቀ፡ ዲያቆን፡ ዘከመ፡ ይሠየም።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.40">
<locus from="10v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter40">Ordination of the reader</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#10v"/>በእንተ፡ አናጕንስጢስ፡ ዘይሰየም።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.41">
<locus from="10v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter41">Of virgins</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#10v"/>በእንተ፡ ደናግል።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.42">
<locus from="10v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter42">Of the laity</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#10v"/>በእንተ፡ ሕዝባውያን።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.43">
<locus from="10v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter43">How they should be received</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#10v"/>በእንተ፡ ዘመፍትው፡ ይትወከፉ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.44">
<locus from="4r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter44">How they should be admitted to baptism</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#4r"/>በእንተ፡ ዘከመ፡ ይትወከፉ፡ ለቅዱሳን፡ ጥምቀት፡ እንተ፡ ትከውን።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.45">
<locus from="11r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter45">Of the kiss of peace</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#11r"/>በእንተ፡ ዘከመ፡ ይትወሀብ፡ ሰላመ፡ ምእመናን።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.46">
<locus from="11r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter46">That women should be covered at prayer</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#11r"/>በእንተ፡ ከመ፡ ይትገልበባ፡ ርእሶን፡ አንስት፡ ሶበ፡ ይጼልያ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.47">
<locus from="11r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter47">Of the imposition of hands on catechumens and neophytes</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#11r"/>በእንተ፡ ንኡሰ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ አንብሮ፡ እድ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.48">
<locus from="11v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter48">Of the examination of catechumens and neophytes</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#11v"/>በእንተ፡ ዘመፍትው፡ በኵሉ፡ መከራ፡ ይትወከፍቅዎሙ፡ ለንዑሰ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ወእፎ፡ መፍትው፡ ይኩኑ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.49">
<locus from="11v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter49">Exorcism to be pronounced over neophytes</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#11v"/>ርቅየተ፡ ንዑሰ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ከመ፡ ይትዓወቁ፡ እለ፡ ቦሙ፡ መንፈስ፡ ነኪር።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.50">
<locus from="12r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter50">Of the order of Baptism</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#12r"/>በእንተ፡ ሥርዓተ፡ ጥምቀት፡ ዘይትገበር፡ ለመሃይምናን።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.51">
<locus from="12r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter51">Prayer of Unction (after Baptism)</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#12r"/>ጸሎተ፡ ቅብዓተ፡ በልሳን።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.52">
<locus from="12v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter52">Of the order of the Holy Eucharist</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#12v"/>በእንተ፡ ሥርዓት፡ እንተ፡ ትትገበር፡ ዲበ፡ ጵርስፎራ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.53">
<locus from="12v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter53">Of Pentecost</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#4r"/>በእንተ፡ ጰንተቈስጤ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.54">
<locus from="13r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter54">Of those who are invited with the bishop (to consume the sacred elements)</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#13r"/>በእንተ፡ እለ፡ ምስለ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ተፀውዑ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.55">
<locus from="13r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter55">Of fruits which are offered</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#13r"/>በእንተ፡ ፍሬ፡ ዘያበውዑ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.56">
<locus from="13r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter56">Of the order of a wedding</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#13r"/>በእንተ፡ ጾታ፡ መርዓት፡ ዘቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.57">
<locus from="13r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter57">That the Holy Eucharist is to be sent to a neophyte who is sick</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#13r"/>በእንተ፡ ከመ፡ ይሰዱ፡ አኩቴተ፡ ለንዑሰ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ድውይም።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.58">
<locus from="13v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter58">Of those who die in poverty</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#13v"/>በእንተ፡ ለእመቦ፡ ዘሞተ፡ ነዳይ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.59">
<locus from="13v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter59">Of the prayers of the people</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#13v"/>በእንተ፡ ዘከመ፡ ይጸልዩ፡ ሕዝብ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.60">
<locus from="13v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2461Testam#Chapter60">Of the receiving of the Holy Eucharist by the faithful</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#13v"/>በእንተ፡ ዘከመ፡ ይትመጠው፡ አኰቴተ፡ ምእመናን።</incipit>
<explicit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#13v"/>ወሶቤሃ፡ ወደቅነ፡ ወሰገድነ፡ ሎቱ፡ እንዘ፡ ንብል፡ ስብሐት፡ ለከ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ዘብርሃን፡ ስሙ፡ ዘወሀብከነ፡ ዘእንተ፡ ታፈቅር፡ ከመ፡ ንኩን፡ ከማከ፡ ንሕነ፡ ወኵሎ፡ ዘተሰምዓከ፡
ወተናጊሮ፡ ምስሌነ፡ ዘንተ፡ ኵሎ፡ ወወሀበነ፡ ሥልጣነ፡ ፍትሕ፡ ወኃይል፡ ብዙኅ፡ ወዓርገ፡ እምኔነ፡ ሰላሞ፡ ኃዲጎ፡ ለነ። ዮሐንስ፡ ወጴጥሮስ፡ ወማቴዎስ፡ ጸሐፍዎ፡ ለዝ፡ ኪዳን፡ እንዘ፡ ያጽሕፎሙ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ እግዚእነ፡
ወፈነዉ፡ በአርአያዝ፡ ኪዳን፡ ግፅወ፡ እምኢየሩሳሌም፡ ደሲቴዎስ፡ ወሲላስ፡ ወመግኖስ፡ ወአቂላስ፡ እለ፡ ኃረዩ፡ ለመላእክት፡ ኵሎ፡ በሓውርተ።</explicit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

